General.Name: Heimstaden AB Pfd.
General.Description: Heimstaden AB (publ) engages in the ownership, development, and management of residential properties in Sweden, Germany, Denmark, the Netherlands, the Czech Republic, Norway, Iceland, Finland, the United Kingdom, and Poland. The company was incorporated in 2004 and is based in Malmö, Sweden. Heimstaden AB (publ) is a subsidiary of Fredensborg AS.
